{"tid":2101713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[手足爆料」慈雲山港泰廢老院向衛生署講假證供隱暪疫情","createTime":"2020-07-10T04:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T17:53:30.000Z","uid":30868,"like":511,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"16a92134fd4d2fb26149a4b620b76d5a9777201b","tid":2101713,"uid":30868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"我係永發大廈居民 住港泰護老院樓上 佢地向衛生署講大話 為左保住半間老人院既生意<br />\n<br />\n港泰護老院向衛生署講 地下層（爆到啪啪聲）同 一樓二樓係分開運作 兩邊員工唔會穿梭<br />\n<br />\n但佢老味我地班居民就日日見到佢地係地下 住客大堂 一樓 二樓穿梭工作 扔垃圾 送餐 我地認得一個男員工 黑皮膚黑框眼鏡食煙既成日出出入入 係大爆發之前佢地一直都係咁做 仲話地下同一+二樓無關係<br />\n<br />\n其實廢老院員工一定要穿過住客大堂 用住客電梯（有三架 單層 雙層 全層）先可以由地下去一同二樓工作<br />\n<br />\n依家我地好撚怕成幢大爆發 仆街廢老院為左繼續經營而同衛生署講大話<br />\n<br />\n保𧙗我地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d376ec1c61091ac5c80c6feaa752685e1742c1","tid":2101713,"uid":94591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"推到上報"},{"pid":"547b03dc1b9039c1400ab1ca661b2f9e67bcec0c","tid":2101713,"uid":84303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"記者朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b9ed4e78cebcceedf64868f6b58cd13b523bec","tid":2101713,"uid":33437,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:08:11.000Z","msg":"報蘋果啦，<br />\n隨時收幾皮報料費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fe6f6b185fa3e789c3b2dde5e2a39f2c46be75","tid":2101713,"uid":229923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c6c964a48d9d1e24a12d33f3d6200c837c747f","tid":2101713,"uid":30868,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"91b9ed4e78cebcceedf64868f6b58cd13b523bec","tid":2101713,"uid":33437,"like":75,"di