258c808aeae4d0ef80f48befde01c694b","tid":2101713,"uid":269706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16a92134fd4d2fb26149a4b620b76d5a9777201b","tid":2101713,"uid":30868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"我係永發大廈居民 住港泰護老院樓上 佢地向衛生署講大話 為左保住半間老人院既生意<br />\n<br />\n港泰護老院向衛生署講 地下層（爆到啪啪聲）同 一樓二樓係分開運作 兩邊員工唔會穿梭<br />\n<br />\n但佢老味我地班居民就日日見到佢地係地下 住客大堂 一樓 二樓穿梭工作 扔垃圾 送餐 我地認得一個男員工 黑皮膚黑框眼鏡食煙既成日出出入入 係大爆發之前佢地一直都係咁做 仲話地下同一+二樓無關係<br />\n<br />\n其實廢老院員工一定要穿過住客大堂 用住客電梯（有三架 單層 雙層 全層）先可以由地下去一同二樓工作<br />\n<br />\n依家我地好撚怕成幢大爆發 仆街廢老院為左繼續經營而同衛生署講大話<br />\n<br />\n保𧙗我地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"其實你可以打去衛生防護中心篤灰<br />\n連登出PO有撚用咩"},{"pid":"ed9c147029782dee052b5d0a515a1210b5d1224b","tid":2101713,"uid":13879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"去警署報警啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁仆乖"},{"pid":"ebdc056e9dc06e6ead292e22453585158e2a880f","tid":2101713,"uid":204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b536bdee4065948ccc8a824ba14aeb39ea898869","tid":2101713,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"香港搞安老院係一盤穩賺嘅生意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"只要夠無良"},{"pid":"04c88d3e1ff0ccd4dd0b0a8381d1ec91cf1dd64b","tid":2101713,"uid":227297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b9b1c122c3fb21ca82375f6f7cb2328954c8bb9","tid":2101713,"uid":163883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4934d74eee43cf1ef66e7cd590a00b519cff414a","tid":2101713,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a92134fd4d2fb26149a4b620b76d5a9777201b","ti